血不少。」胡郭笑介绍到，600 多万元先后到手，钱一到，马上去囤黄金。 黄金消费火热！一城 200 米路开 15 家金店，有店铺买黄金送钻石券、有店家卖两套房押注黄金"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-afcb1cc58623c4165515f7ef9e039fff_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "10 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/636492257"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImZmGovbitZlPEAMaCTEwMzcyMTE2OSDw56OsBjAAODNAK3IJNjM2NDkyMjU3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1703551004.534664", "card_id": "Q_636657677", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "暴雪中国回应国服回归「目前没有可以分享的信息或者更新」，国服回归可能性有多大？面临哪些问题？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "12 月 25 日消息，针对媒体报道的网易暴雪重新合作，代理引进《魔兽世界》国服版一事，暴雪中国表示：「我们这边目前没有可以分享的信息或者更新。」暴雪中国回应国服回归：目前没有可以分享的信息或者更新 - 钛媒体官方网站"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-81fa43928ff03a2c4363f1c07c5ad9d1_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "10 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/636657677"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImZmGovbitZlPEAMaCTEwMzc1Nzg4OCCFl6isBjAAOBhALHIJNjM2NjU3Njc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1703551004.535402", "card_id": "Q_617558835", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么不能往体内注水？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在医院打针、注射疫苗都是往身体内注射液体，为什么不能往身体里注射饮用水呢？比如可乐雪碧"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e0e3f57da8dc5b0c706300d18714c4ae_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "10 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/617558835"}